quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  15,71,"Naboola mbu: “Bano nabakhana banje, (itse ebahelesie mubateshie), toto enywe nimuli abakholanga.""
  15,72,"Nditsuba khulubaka lulwo mbu: “Abo bali mubumesi bwabu, nibanyakhananga eshikhaya.”"
  15,73,"Mana eshinyasio shioluyoka nishibabukula mumabwibwi."
  15,74,"Mana nikhukhola hasi wabu okhuba hekulu. Mana nikhubakwisilia ifula yamachina keliloba lia mumulilo."
  15,75,"Toto mu ako kalimwo ameeko khubandu baretsanga amakhuwa khushichelo."
  15,76,"Ne toto tsingongo etso tsili khutsinjila tsiliwo tsiburungwakhwo."
  15,77,"Toto mu ako kalimwo ameeko khubasuubili."
  15,78,"Ne toto abandu bomushitsimi bali ababii."
  15,79,"Mana nikhubahelesia eshinyasio, ne ebialo bibili bino bili khunjila ili habulafu."
  15,80,"Ne toto Abandu ba Hijri bayingasia Abarumwa."
  15,81,"Ne nikhubahelesia ebimanyisio biefu, nabo nibalabukulamwo oluchendo tawe."
  15,82,"Ne bakwotanga tsingulu nibakasia tsinzu nomulembe."
  15,83,"Mana eshinyasio shioluyoka nishibabukula mumabwibwi."
  15,84,"Mana akabakholanga nikalabakhonyakhwo shiosishiosi tawe."
  15,85,"Ne shikhwalonga likulu nende eshialo, nende ebili hakari wabio tawe halali khubwatoto. Ne toto indukho iliula, kho leshela okhuleshela okhulayi."
  15,86,"Toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye omuloonji watoto, Omumanyi muno."
  15,87,"Ne toto khwakhwelesia tsinyaali saba tsisomungwa ebise nebise, nende Ikurani yoluyali."
  15,88,"Ne olakhosia tsimoni tsitsio khukalia akakhwahelesia emikanda chindi mubo, khandi olababelelela tawe. Ne wishilie abasuubili olubaa lulwo (lwetsimbabaasi)."
  15,89,"Ne boola mbu: “Toto esie nesie omwikanyilisi, omwinoosi owahabulafu.""
  15,90,"Shingala khweshilia balia (eshinyasio bosi) abekaba emikanda (okhwikalila obusalamu)."